@@TJvImageList.Mode
Summary
  Sets the mode of the image list.
 
Description
  Set Mode to one of the following values
- imClassic
 The image list acts as TImageList. The Filename, Picture and ResourceIds properties are ignored - 
imPicture
The FileName and Picture property are used.
- imResourceIds
The ResourceIds property is used.
 
See Also
  Picture,FileName,ResourceIds
 
